3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques for face detection. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with real-time face detection on mobile devices, which involves multimedia processing. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with cryptography or security, but it is still possible as the paper deals with the performance of face detection on public benchmarks.
